Style "FvwmTaskBar" NoTitle, BorderWidth 1, HandleWidth 1, StaysOnTop, Sticky, WindowListSkip, CirculateSkip, NoIcon

AddToFunc DeiconifyRaiseAndFocus
+ I Iconify off
+ I Raise
+ I Focus

*FvwmTaskBar: Action Click1 DeiconifyRaiseAndFocus
*FvwmTaskBar: Action Click2 Iconify on
*FvwmTaskBar: Action Click3 Lower
*FvwmTaskBar: UseSkipList
*FvwmTaskBar: PageOnly
*FvwmTaskBar: ColorSet 3
*FvwmTaskBar: IconColorSet 2
*FvwmTaskBar: AutoStick
*FvwmTaskBar: AutoHide
